caption.paragraph:
FIGURES 1-6. Nuisiana arboris (Marples 1959). 1. Male pedipalp, ventral view ; 2 . Male pedipalp, retrolateral view; 3. Epigynum, ventral view; 4. Internal genitalia, ventral view; 5. Internal genitalia, dorsal view; 6. Schematic course of internal ducts.
Scale bars for figures 1, 2 = 1.0 mm, 3-5 = 0.5 mm . Abbreviations used: C, cymbium; E, embolus; MA, median apophysis;
RTA, retrolateral tibial apophysis; ML, median lobe.

